text: The Haga Church () is an church building in the town of Gothenburg in Sweden. It belongs to Gothenburg Haga Parish of the Church of Sweden. The church was opened on Advent Sunday, 27 November, 1859. ==References== ==Other websites== * information from the Gothenburg Haga Parish Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Churches in Gothenburg Category:Buildings and structures completed in the 19th century
title: Haga Church
